{"tid":137461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老衝紅燈　累司機閃避不及炒車","createTime":"2017-02-27T23:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T02:22:01.000Z","uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac079c0760003a2032935657cf416eeb0428d7ee","tid":137461,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160221/photo/bkn-20160221170142694-0221_00822_001_01p.jpg?20160221181350\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160221%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160221170142694-0221_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20160221181350&h=0385e9ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有人都要遵守法律，不管是孩童、大人，還是老人家，因為如果犯了法，不僅僅影響自己，隨時會害到別人！今日澳門有一名老婦被指衝紅燈，連累電單車司機閃避不及而炒車。<br />\n<br />\n網民Marco Ma&lrm;今早在facebook群組「澳門道路情報」發貼，指一名老婦過馬路時衝紅燈，<span style=\"color: red;\">一名電單車司機為急閃避她而炒車，老婦受驚跌倒後，自行起身，繼續衝紅燈，離開現場</span>。相中穿深藍外套的男司機半跪在地，身旁的綿羊仔翻側，而被指亂過路的老婦正橫過馬路。<br />\n<br />\n事件引來熱議，多數網民都狠批涉事長者「唔抵幫」，斥責倚老賣老行為極要不得！也有人替電單車司機抱不平，慨嘆他行衰運，老婦害他撞車，他罵也不是，不罵一定滿腔怨氣無法發洩。另有人指不少長者都很自私，沒有想過他們不跟交通規則過路，不止容易發生意外，還會累及無辜，今日的事就是最佳例子。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nNadia Bonita：呀婆可能六十年前係賽跑冠軍？<br />\n<br />\nSamsonEmperor Cheong： 1. 捉住個阿婆，告佢過失傷人囉 / 2. 司機自認倒霉<br />\n<br />\nAlan Sam：阿婆走得快，一定有古怪。<br />\n<br />\nDavis Tou：呀婆側面霸氣依然<br />\n<br />\nSn Ake：阿婆大叫：我條命我自己負責，你揸車嘅有責任讓人&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;（曲線）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160221/mobile/bkn-20160221170142694-0221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160221%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20160221170142694-0221_00822_001.html&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F17%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f3d244aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160221/mobile/bkn-20160221170142694-0221_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6d0f7840af51d3a7e911999f063318d3de8e806","tid":137461,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:27:59.000Z","msg":"廢老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fde188f671d6e7cb0f3d55dcab95e211eb078f5","tid":137461,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"冚家剷 一陣死咗又俾人入不小心駕駛導致他人死亡"},{"pid":"b478dbe7c0f1fc3d565ea3c444aee9c04a342f9f","tid":137461,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:28:17.000Z","msg":"死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7434528c6f424e3eb926c1ee363f67609c0c345f","tid":137461,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冚家剷 一陣死咗又俾人入不小心駕駛導致他人死亡</blockquote><br />\n已經試過<br />\n有單車死左個阿婆個巴士司機被判監"},{"pid":"9f448643e221679f60e4582ca8930b6a4ea69682","tid":137461,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:32:28.000Z","msg":"之前學車又係見到個廢老想衝紅燈<br />\n最慘佢又衝唔哂<br />\n行左兩步又停左係度,之後仲凸枝柺杖出黎好似想示意叫我停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934194582ce4ac752f822dd27296bc69eb28cfa1","tid":137461,"uid":22481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:36:47.000Z","msg":"不捐血 不捐錢 不讓坐"},{"pid":"e34f061710dbe18d87ff7a71e9ab5248940dbad1","tid":137461,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:36:53.000Z","msg":"廢老is everywhere"},{"pid":"28284e4d166309324b2e4c00848b8f64199766fc","tid":137461,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:03:35.000Z","msg":"老人家都想蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3708109a6f149fe22020c0638eb5c8f5b56f6a35","tid":137461,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:16:41.000Z","msg":"死撚晒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585d78b21450a00173744ff03